{"tid":2191881,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖」「推介」在名建築裏吃午餐","createTime":"2020-09-06T17:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:13:32.000Z","uid":267974,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf4fbae5d2fd1ccf3e02892d4bfdfff4a66c5d6","tid":2191881,"uid":267974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYbktYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYbktYT.png&h=088f68ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNMDZ5z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNMDZ5z.jpg&h=f4be4687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推介下日劇清新小品  怪叔叔同美少女嘅邂逅 佢地講野唔多 但向建築空間內彼此連繫 發覺真係靚嘅野 係唔駛講太多野 不過唔好夜深睇 佢啲咖喱飯會令人個肚咕咕聲<br />\n<br />\n原來frank Lloyd Wright 向日本有建築 類似prairie house 巴打們唔好錯過～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360d8948dde90bf993a4686d8e65c76c6c5dc70d","tid":2191881,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"香港?"},{"pid":"662e680e7c59762cda23d34509f6e14e38ed020f","tid":2191881,"uid":267974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"360d8948dde90bf993a4686d8e65c76c6c5dc70d","tid":2191881,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"香港?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"係日劇黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885d00b6d71fcd60de09156c28900503af52de30","tid":2191881,"uid":249026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:46:02.000Z","msg":"好正<br />\n唔